### Admin - buscar Qhapaq con contactos
GET http://localhost:4004/odata/v4/admin/Suppliers?$filter=name eq 'Qhapaq Energy Maintenance'&$expand=contacts

### Admin - PATCH parcial Qhapaq
PATCH http://localhost:4004/odata/v4/admin/Suppliers({{qhapaqSupplierId}})
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "riskScore": 63,
  "riskLevel": "MEDIUM"
}

### Admin - verificar PATCH parcial
GET http://localhost:4004/odata/v4/admin/Suppliers({{qhapaqSupplierId}})?$select=ID,name,country,taxId,email,phone,status,riskScore,riskLevel,category_ID&$expand=category,contacts

### Admin - PUT incompleto Qhapaq
PUT http://localhost:4004/odata/v4/admin/Suppliers({{qhapaqSupplierId}})
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Qhapaq Energy Maintenance Updated",
  "country": "Peru",
  "riskScore": 82,
